<h3><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif">What? define.&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p>def :&nbsp; action or process of causing someone to adopt beliefs&nbsp; on political or social issues which advocates complete&nbsp;change&nbsp;<br />
<span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif">Not legally defined&nbsp; =&gt; MHA approved RnD on 'status of radicalisation'. (nov 2020)</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif">Why a challenge?&nbsp;</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif">Problem often not recognised.</span></p>
